(1099, 1246404785, NULL, 1246197600, '1', 2, 4, 'c', '26', '', '', 'Coolmores', '', 1, 7, 1, 21, '3cm strip of cyan missing through the top of the Coolmore ad, this cyan strip missing is evident through out the form.\r\nCAn we find out numbers and how and why etc', 24, NULL, 'The problem was due to the cyan blanket cylinder clutching in the wrong position resulting in the blanket gapno providing impression in the image area.\r\nThis has never been seen before and is being inestigated as to how it could technically occur. This would have been impossible for the press team team to identify.\r\nAll copies affected.', 'Closed', '', 'many', '0', '0', '0', 1, 1),
