(1219, 1341506590, NULL, 1341496800, '1', 1, 1, 'D', '82', '', '', '', '', 0, 23, 3, 21, 'Damaged blanket on page 82 on the Sydney Ford add, cyan blanket damaged, 50,000 copies printed before press crew noticed the damage and a further 10,000 printed as production was running late and only 2 out of the 3 presses were running.', 1, '23', 'blanket damaged, 50,000 copies printed before press crew noticed the damage and a further 10,000 printed as production was running late and only 2 out of the 3 presses were running.', 'Closed', '', '', '0', '0', '1', 1, 0),
