(1229, 1345436422, NULL, 1344952800, '2', 16, 1, 'C', '45', 'Starr Partners', '', '', '', 1, 3, 2, 7, 'Starr Partners Principal has complained regarding the reproduction of page 45 in the Parramatta Advertiser. The Blue is over inked with Cyan and the registration is slighty out also. They have 7 full pages side by side and the other 6 are consistant, not to sure why page 45 looks so different??', 1, '20', 'Lee,\r\n\r\nUnfortunately, the check copies show that the whole run is affected. This will be passed onto the afternoon shift crew responsible for an explanation as to why this may have occurred. Marty, Simon or Garth will respond further when they have more information.\r\n\r\nSteve', 'Closed', '', 'Whole run', '0', '1', '0', 1, 0),
