(1367, 1377732503, NULL, 1377612000, '2', 7, 1, 'F1', '49', 'One Agency', '', '', '', 1, 3, 2, 6, 'Client is unhappy with the reproduction of there ad. Rego is out which has created a Yellow keyline around their Orange logo', 1, '32', 'Hi Lee,\r\nThe Liverpool Leader press check copies have been reviewed and the yellow key-line is evident throughout all the check copies. The 5,000 to 10,000 check copies show the registration is closer but the key-line is still visible.   \r\nIn reviewing all the pages printing on that plate cylinder, unfortunately the crew has had to manage the registration to run all pages as close as possible. The production was run on F Press unit 3, this unit had a blanket re-dress 9 million impressions ago. The registration on this unit will need to be investigated in the form of a registration test print. Once the test is complete the results will be communicated. In the meantime the unit has been removed from production, unless a 5 unit production is required.\r\nIf further information is required, please do hesitate to contact me.\r\nRegards,\r\nIan', 'InProgress', '', '', '0', '0', '0', 1, 0),
