(1389, 1380670424, NULL, 1380549600, '2', 15, 1, 'E', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 3, 2, 18, 'Macarthur Chronicle has a lap which wasn\\''t requested and 3/4 Ribbon inside the book has been affected with the right hand page having the fold through it and text cant be read without having to pull centre out.', 1, '16', 'Hi Lee,\r\n\r\nWe have checked all check copies. Unfortunately all copies appear to have lap. The paperwork had indicated no lap this was mistake by avro & night E press crew. \r\n\r\nWe will address this issue with the press crew responsible as they should questioned why there was a lap as this does not match paperwork. In any doubt, crew can radio call to publishing to double check LAP is or isn’t required.\r\n\r\nWith recent registration issues of the News Local mastheads the press crews are placing extra attention to keep this issue to a minimum but missed this one.\r\n\r\n', 'Closed', '', 'All', '0', '1', '0', 1, 0),
