(1396, 1381275726, NULL, 1380549600, '2', 24, 1, '', '16, 57', 'LJ Hooker, Merc RE', '', '', '', 1, 3, 2, 6, 'LJ Hooker & Merc RE have complained regarding the rego and the effect that has on their images and some text. Is whole run affected? Sorry not sure what press it\\''s on, it\\''s not in spine', 1, '32', 'Hi Lee,\r\nAll Hill Shire Real Estate QC check copies show a black registration issue from the 20,000 check copy onwards, for the remainder of the run.\r\nIn reviewing the imposition, the production was run on F Press all units. Page 16 and 57 were positioned on unit 1, this unit was redressed on 18/09/13 and centre path roller replaced on the 17/09/2013.\r\nThe blankets on this unit have been inspected today, a slight gap was found, which can cause web creasing, in turn affecting registration. These blankets will be adjusted and re-torqued today. The press crew involved reported issues with no scans or tiffs to run QI, however there is no report of registration issues. The press crew members involved will also go through performance feedback counselling, once further investigating is complete.\r\nPlease let me know if you require any further information.\r\nRegards,\r\nIan Ford ', 'Closed', '', '48,000', '0', '0', '0', 1, 0),
