(1405, 1382310211, NULL, 1381755600, '2', 15, 1, 'C', '48', 'First National', '', '', '', 1, 3, 2, 6, 'This has been ongoing, 4th time they have complained regarding the head shots, registration is out and their eyes are affected, looking like they are rolling at the back of their heads. Are all copies affected? ', 1, '32', 'Hi Lee,\r\nAll the QC check copies for Macarthur have been reviewed and all copies show a slight registration issue on page 48. Some copies are worse than others, however it\\''s only out of registration a small amount. \r\nAll the pages printed in that plate position show a slight registration problem, which needs further investigation but could mean a loose blanket. \r\nPress crews involved will be reviewing the QC check copies along with the clients feedback during this weeks team meeting. It will also be communicated in the form of a quality folder located on each press, which contains adverts that require more focus. \r\nPlease contact me if you require any further information. \r\nRegards,\r\nIan', 'Closed', '', '77,525', '0', '0', '0', 1, 0),
