(1414, 1383800027, NULL, 1383224400, '2', 21, 1, '', '36', 'First National', '', '', '', 1, 3, 2, 6, 'Client not happy with registration, the magenta plate is out quite a bit. My copy is the same. Are all copies affected?', 1, '23', 'Looking at the check copies here, there are no copies with the magenta rego out on page 36.\r\nThe press report stated that the press was pulled up to replace page 3 and 21. Page 36 was paired with 21. Our 1st check copies are at approx 14,000 copies.\r\nSumming up the 1st  14,000 could have copies with varying degrees of rego issues. Sample copies are here if you or the customer requires them.\r\n', 'Closed', '', '14000', '0', '0', '0', 1, 0),
