(1423, 1385511650, NULL, 1385038800, '2', 21, 1, 'E', '57', 'Century 21', '', '', '', 1, 3, 2, 10, 'The Client Century 21\\''s copy of Central Coast Real Estate has Magenta ink catch up throughout the page. My QC copy also has Magenta ink catch up. Can you see how many copies affected? Thanks', 1, '32', 'Hi Lee,\r\nAll the QC check copies have been reviewed, the catch up on page 57 is evident until the 8,600 check copy. Which would mean the first 8,600 copies were affected by catch up. All check copies after that don’t show any signs of catch up. The check copies are available if required.\r\nThe production was produced on E Press and information from the press crews indicate there was technical issues with QI press control cameras (which control the water on the press) and further issues with the forwarding station, which delayed production by over 3 hours.\r\nPress crew members involved will be receiving performance feedback on the production, with the outcomes of those conversations to be recorded in feedback logs.\r\nPlease contact me if you require any further information.\r\nRegards,\r\nIan\r\n', 'Closed', '', '8,600', '1', '0', '1', 1, 0),
