(1428, 1386056424, NULL, 1386075600, '2', 8, 1, 'D', '18', '', '', '', '', 0, 28, 3, 22, 'Dexus property group, ad & address is obscured by a black bar running through it. This error has appeared 3 weeks in a row.', 1, '7', 'We have found there’s a bug in the Dalim normalisation process, and we’re dealing with Dalim working on the bug fix.\r\nThere is an update ready to fix this particular issue with a change of workflow, but the new workflow has another bug which would create further issues with fixing over inked material.\r\nWe are also speaking to customer to help us by outlining the specific font “Avante Guarde Book” this is a band aid but hopefully rectify the issue with that particular client.\r\n\r\nThis is not an easy problem to pick up, as these view correctly in all QC tools this issue happens at the rip when sent to press.\r\n\r\nMark Soulie\r\n\r\n', 'Closed', '', '', '0', '1', '0', 1, 0),
