(1431, 1386301001, NULL, 1386162000, '2', 4, 1, '', '40', '', '', 'Laing & Simmons', '', 1, 11, 2, 10, 'The same ad has shown catchup and setoff for the last 3 weeks both in QC copies and the client copies. Please advise quantity and also flag with the press crew that this ad runs every week and it would be a $ loss to let this happen 4 weeks in a row.\r\nThanks.', 1, '32', 'Hi Scott, \r\n\r\nAll the QC check copies have been reviewed, the catch up on page 40 is evident throughout the run. Some of the check copies the catch up is more visible the others, however we would have to indicate the entire run was affected.\r\n\r\nThe production was produced on C Press and information from the press crews indicates there was no technical issues on press. Press crew members involved will be receiving performance feedback on the production, with the outcomes of those conversations to be recorded in feedback logs. There will also be communication on the customer being the focus of all our productions, with Hornsby Advocate having extra focus. \r\n\r\nPlease contact me if you require any further information.\r\n\r\nRegards,\r\nIan', 'Closed', '', '51582', '0', '0', '0', 1, 0),
