(1446, 1392072132, NULL, 1392037200, '1', 1, 4, 'E', '27, 38', '', '', '', '', 0, 36, 1, 7, 'Both page 27 and 38 appear to have a very low black ink density. Pls check if the whole run was affected.', 1, '32', 'Hi Marcel,\r\n\r\nAll press check copies from last night’s Telegraph production from both production lines have been reviewed. All the check copies show no sign of low black ink density. \r\n\r\nThe press reports have also been reviewed and there was no indication that crews had any press technical issues.  \r\n\r\nIs it possible to obtain the copies? The production was run on E and F Line and the copies can be used as part of feedback during this week’s team meetings, with the outcomes registered in the feedback performance log for those press crew members involved.  \r\n\r\nPlease let us know if you require any further information, the press check copies are available if required.\r\n\r\nRegards,\r\nIan Ford \r\n', 'Closed', '', '', '0', '0', '1', 1, 0),
(1447, 1392098733, NULL, 1392037200, '2', 15, 2, 'C', '44-45', 'Combined Real Estate', '', '', '', 1, 3, 2, 2, 'Client has complained about the black strip at the bottom is washed out. Checked my copy and the black ink density is quite low from half way down the page. Is the whole Camden run affected?', 1, '32', 'Hi Lee,\r\n\r\nAll press check copies from the Macarthur Chronicle production have been reviewed. All the check copies show no sign of low black ink density on page 44 and 45 (see attached). \r\n\r\nThe press reports have also been reviewed, the crew reported an issue with the auto black ink fill during the Camden edition, which stopped production and Reliability attended and replaced the ink pump. That being the case, the most likely cause is the customer and yourself have received a start-up copy, before all the black ink was back up to density.      \r\n\r\nIs it possible to obtain the copies? The production was run on C Line and the copies can be used as part of feedback during this week’s team meetings, with the outcomes registered in the feedback performance log for those press crew members involved.  \r\n\r\nPlease let us know if you require any further information, the press check copies are available if required.\r\n\r\nRegards,\r\nIan Ford \r\n', 'Closed', '', '500', '0', '0', '1', 1, 0),
