(1474, 1400550330, NULL, 1400335200, '1', 13, 5, '', '125', 'Rydges', '', '', '', 1, 3, 1, 26, 'Client is unhappy with the Hickeys in the ad, is whole run like this? Pic attached.', 1, '32', 'Hi Lee,\r\n\r\nAll press check copies of the Sunday Telegraph (publication date - 18/05/14) across all presses have been review with mixed results.\r\n\r\nE Press check copies show the same hickies as per your attached image from the 36,000 check copy through to the end of the run, in total 120,000 copies affected.\r\n\r\nC and D Press check copies show minimum hickies - 228,845 copies partially affected.\r\n\r\nF Press check copies show no signs of hickies - 85,838 copies not affected.\r\n\r\nSPC are currently working with consumable suppliers to find a root cause of the hickies. Further testing was conducted last week with the results being presented on Friday. As soon as more information is available it will be communicated.\r\n\r\nPress check copies are available if required.\r\n\r\nPlease let us know if you require any further information.\r\n\r\nRegards,\r\n\r\nIan', 'Closed', '', '120,000', '0', '0', '0', 1, 0),
