(1558, 1445987943, NULL, 1445864400, '2', 24, 1, 'C', '97', 'McGrath', '', '', '', 1, 3, 2, 6, 'MCgrath have complained regarding the registration of their ad on page 97. Text is quite hard to read. Please see attached. Is the whole run affected?', 1, '32', 'Hi Lee,\r\n\r\nAll press check copies have been reviewed and the McGrath ad on page 97 shows slightly affected registration. \r\n\r\nDue to the ad being four colour reverse type any registration slightly out, will cause the font to look darker and possibly harder to read.  \r\n\r\n ', 'Closed', '', '59,143', '0', '0', '0', 1, 0),
