(1564, 1454975014, NULL, 1454072400, '1', 10, 1, '', '7', '', '', 'Shapiro', '', 0, 7, 1, 9, 'Client has complained about the reproduction of their insertion in the The review, their ad specifically the statue is very red and lacking detail- they have sent over comparison prints from other publications SMH etc the statue is gold, Proofing the file out also is gold and what i would expect from the file supplied.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Open', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 0),
(1565, 1457489017, NULL, 1457442000, '2', 14, 1, 'E', '3,13,28,38', '', '', '', '', 0, 53, 2, 10, 'THIS IS FOR CENTRAL SYDNEY WHICH IS NOT IN THE PUBLICATION SELECTION LIST. \r\n\r\nPlease let us numbers affected.', 1, '32', 'Hi Godly,\r\n\r\nAll press check copies have been reviewed and no copies show any signs of catch up. The press crew that ran the production have indicated a clean production run with no faults relating to catch up. \r\n\r\nIf reports and check copies indicate no catch up, there\\''s two possible causes as to how copies have made it to the market place with catch up. With both possible causes up to 500 copies could be affect.  \r\n\r\n1. Start up copies - the press crew have released the waste control button to early allowing copies with catch up to go out to publishing. \r\n\r\n2. QI water control - QI continuously scans the web while in production looking for imperfections like catch up. If catch up is detected QI will increase water values within the range of 500 copies to rectify.\r\n\r\nIf more copies were affected it would have shown up in the check copies, the press crew would have been reporting issues and stopping the press due to catch up.\r\n\r\nIf you require any further information please contact me.\r\n\r\nThank you,\r\n\r\nIan\r\n\r\n ', 'Closed', '', '500', '0', '1', '0', 1, 0),
